snippet: Peter Uihlein, a former Oklahoma State star whose play at the Irish Open and other windy European tournaments has surprised some observers, is determined to forge his own path.
abstract: Profile of golfer Peter Uihlein, former Oklahoma State star whose play at the Irish Open and other windy European golf tournaments has surprised some observers; Uihlein is determined to forge his own path, honing his game in tournaments abroad.
lead_paragraph: Peter Uihlein, a former Oklahoma State star whose play at the Irish Open and other windy European tournaments has surprised some observers, is determined to forge his own path.

headline.main: American Golfer Thrives on the Fairways Less Traveled
headline.print_headline: An American Is Thriving With a Path Less Taken but Well Traveled
